quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  39,32,"E ko hommbo ɓuri tooñde wa on fenuɗo e hoore Allah, maa o fenni goonga kan nde ka arunoo e makko? E wonaa Jahannama woni jaaƴorde yedduɓe ɓen"
  39,33,"On non arduɗo e goonga, o goongini ɗum, ko ɓen woni gomɗuɓe ɓen"
  39,34,"Hino woodani kala ko ɓe faaletee, ka Joomi maɓɓe; ko ɗum njoɓdi moƴƴinooɓe ɓen"
  39,35,"fii no Allah yawtirana ɓe, ko ɓuri bonnde e ko ɓe golli kon, O yoɓitira ɓe njoɓdi maɓɓe ndin, ko ɓuri moƴƴude e ko ɓe gollaynoo kon"
  39,36,"Allah siforaali yonugol jeyaaɗo Makko on? Hiɓe hulɓinire ɗin ɗi wonaa Mo. Kala mo Allah majjini, haray fewnoowo alanaa mo"
  39,37,"Kala non mo Allah fewni, majjinoowo mo alaa. Allah siforaali wonnde Fooluɗo, Jom lepte"
  39,38,"Pellet, si a lamndike ɓe: \"Ko hommbo tagi kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin?\", ma ɓe wi'u: \"Ko Allah\". Maaku: \"Yeetee lam fii ɗin ɗi rewoton gaanin Allah, si Allah faandanike lam lorra, hara ɗi huncanay lam lorra Makko kan? Maa si O faandanike lam yurmeende, taw si ɗi haɗay lam yurmeende Makko nden? Maaku: \"Allah yonii lam, ko e Makko hoolnotooɓe ɓen tuuginotoo"
  39,39,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo yimɓe am, gollee e laawol mon, min ko e [laawol am] mi gollirta. Aray ka anndon"
  39,40,"ko hommbo lepte hoynayɗe aroyat e muuɗum, lepte duumiiɗe jippoo e makko"